OL,3,CEmergency services searching for
OL,4,Cmissing boy at lake recover body
OL,6,FEmergency services have confirmed
OL,7,Fthey've recovered a body from a
OL,8,FLeicestershire lake while searching
OL,9,Ffor a missing teenage boy.
OL,11,FIt was reported that the boy entered
OL,12,FMeynell Lake, in Fosse Way in Syston,
OL,13,Fwith police being called just after
OL,14,F1:30pm on Thursday (June 25th).
OL,16,FLeicestershire Police attended along
OL,17,Fwith Leicestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,18,FService and East Midlands Ambulance
OL,19,FService.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
