OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782648717
OL,3,CEmergency services searching for
OL,4,Cmissing boy at lake recover body
OL,6,FThey said initial searches were
OL,7,Fcarried out, and police divers were
OL,8,Fcalled in.
OL,10,FThere is no suggestion of any
OL,11,Fsuspicious circumstances, and
OL,12,Fdetectives say a file will be prepared
OL,13,Ffor HM Coroner.
OL,15,FWreake Valley Academy, which is a
OL,16,Fnearby school, confirmed that the boy
OL,17,Fwas one of their students.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
