OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782648717
OL,3,CEmergency services searching for
OL,4,Cmissing boy at lake recover body
OL,6,FIn a statement, they said: "We are
OL,7,Fdevastated by the loss of one of our
OL,8,Fstudents and our thoughts and deepest
OL,9,Fcondolences are with their family and
OL,10,Ffriends.
OL,12,FThis tragic accident has deeply
OL,13,Faffected everyone at our school and we
OL,14,Fare providing support to students,
OL,15,Fstaff, and families who need it.
OL,17,F"We kindly ask that the privacy of
OL,18,Fthose affected is respected during
OL,19,Fthis extremely difficult time."
